cu.explanation_en: Setting sst to an out-of-range value (1000) will cause invalid SNSSAI configuration and network slice selection failure.

du.explanation_en: Setting nrofDownlinkSymbols to an out-of-range value (100) will cause invalid TDD configuration and symbol allocation issues.
du.explanation_zh: 將 nrofDownlinkSymbols 設定為超出範圍的值 (100)，會導致無效的 TDD 配置，並造成符號分配問題。
